44:07.729 --> 44:10.981
If so, I'm giving them five business days
to try to impress us

44:11.065 --> 44:12.899
with a price for controlling
interest in the agency.

44:12.984 --> 44:14.484
There he is.

44:14.569 --> 44:17.070
There's the man I heard so much about.

44:18.448 --> 44:19.740
Five days to make an offer.

44:19.824 --> 44:22.451
Or you can give me a price,
and I'll pass it on.

44:22.535 --> 44:26.496
No. Let them open the kimono.

44:29.417 --> 44:32.419
Daddy, Daddy, over here!

44:32.503 --> 44:34.546
This water's cold.

44:37.342 --> 44:39.509
Stop splashing.

45:22.053 --> 45:23.929
Hello. lt's Dick Whitman.

45:27.725 --> 45:29.309
Yeah.

45:31.437 --> 45:34.106
I'd love to see you.

45:34.190 --> 45:35.315
Soon.

45:36.734 --> 45:39.194
No. l didn't bring it with me.

45:39.278 --> 45:40.445
Hold on.

